Package: ossec-hids-doc
Architecture: all
Description: documentation for ossec-hids.
 OSSEC is a full platform to monitor and control your systems.
 It mixes together all the aspects of:
  - HIDS (host-based intrusion  detection),
  - log monitoring,
  - SIM/SIEM together.

